    <ThingDef ParentName="BaseHumanMakeableGun">
        <defName>HP_AM_Gun_MeltaGun</defName>
        <label>Astra Militarum meltagun</label>
        <description>Amidst the tumultuous expanses of the Warhammer 40,000 universe, the Astra Militarum Melta Gun emerges as a beacon of concentrated heat and destructive power wielded by the indomitable forces of the Imperium. Forged with precision and purpose, this formidable weapon features a matte-black ceramite alloy construction, a testament to its durability and reliability in the brutal theater of war.\n\nFunctioning as a close-range and anti-armor firearm, the Melta Gun projects concentrated beams of intense thermal energy, capable of liquefying armor and immolating even the most heavily fortified targets. Its design embodies versatility, allowing for devastating assaults on enemy vehicles and structures, making it a critical asset in the strategic repertoire of the Astra Militarum.\n\nEach discharge resonates with a distinctive hiss, heralding the Melta Gun's ability to turn the tide of battle with its unparalleled thermal devastation. In the hands of the disciplined soldiers of the Astra Militarum, this weapon stands as a testament to the Imperium's commitment to overwhelming firepower and technological supremacy in the ceaseless struggle against heresy and alien adversaries in the grim and war-torn galaxy of Warhammer 40,000.</description>
